    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮🕹️ 操作 (※支持键盘／游戏手柄，可在设置中更改)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[↑↓←→ AWSD] - 移动</strong><br><strong>[SPACE Z]</strong> - 出拳 (A)<br><strong>[X C V B]</strong> - 观察 (B) <br>     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✨⭐✨全饲主翘首以盼的猫咪专用动作游戏！✨⭐✨</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轮到你的爱猫踏上旅程了。<br>目标是亲眼看看你经常仰望的那颗“HOSHI”。<br>克服种种困难，你的爱猫最终能否与你一起看到那片星空呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ 观测星星吧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/08ca392f5e885612e466da3e5590b1e7.poster.avif?t=1771025306\" width=248 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/08ca392f5e885612e466da3e5590b1e7.webm?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/08ca392f5e885612e466da3e5590b1e7.mp4?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/beb204e78208629e25472d80d345642d.poster.avif?t=1771025306\" width=250 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/beb204e78208629e25472d80d345642d.webm?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/beb204e78208629e25472d80d345642d.mp4?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用“观察（B）”来观测星空。<strong></strong><br><br><br><br>远方可见的那颗星，不久后将成为降临于此的威胁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ 连接⚽球体制作 Craft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/4ae9d8904c3e125709fb142ab39d02a3.poster.avif?t=1771025306\" width=196 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/4ae9d8904c3e125709fb142ab39d02a3.webm?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/4ae9d8904c3e125709fb142ab39d02a3.mp4?t=1771025306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>　<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/656139720390ec11fcff73f2dc23f8b1.avif?t=1771025306\" width=303 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >周围滚动着球形物体“Minon”。<br>相同颜色的球体可以连接，按下“出拳（A）”即可制作 Craft。<br>根据连接的形状，制作出的 Craft 也会有所不同。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⭐ 迎战各种强敌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/9195dcc2ffe89f10d3af32f7b5e16df9.avif?t=1771025306\" width=250 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/704bdd2bf0db5aa93ec36a5c0c9f8219.avif?t=1771025306\" width=250 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/30caa91208adbfe9321f49e8ae271622.avif?t=1771025306\" width=250 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过观测星空预知威胁的到来，积累关于 Minon 的知识，并熟练运用 Craft，<br>去迎击巨大战舰和精神体等外来生物吧。<br>前所未有的未知战斗正等待着你！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ 丰富的自定义模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・使用 VRM 文件替代主人登场</strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/d970e57ed9ddf43612984dc551307e21.avif?t=1771025306\" width=500 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 .vrm 文件，你可以以“主人”的身分登场于故事中。<br><br><strong>・自定义术语</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以更改游戏故事中的关键用语。<br>将“HOSHI”、“光”、“暗”替换为你喜欢的词语，打造专属于你的世界观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1002470/extras/a47d5f6f762eaf4bcd5552e3d208ba47.avif?t=1771025306\" width=500 height=318 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⭐ 关于实况与直播</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 无论是个人还是法人，均可自由进行游戏实况与直播。<br>允许开启收益化（广告收入、打赏等）。<br>请自行判断并顾及观众的感受。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⭐ <strong>禁止事项</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・严禁将本作图像或音频用于游戏试玩或介绍以外的目的。<br>・严禁利用本作对第三方进行攻击、诽谤或诋毁。<br>・严禁将本作与 R-18、R-18G 等成人向元素结合使用。<br>・严禁将本作用于宗教或政治目的。</p>",
